    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/e1f381c2947fa05886c7430c97f795d9.poster.avif?t=1762688249\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/e1f381c2947fa05886c7430c97f795d9.webm?t=1762688249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/e1f381c2947fa05886c7430c97f795d9.mp4?t=1762688249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/19fc9575a03a4eae7e3b6c8cac8d9221.avif?t=1762688249\" width=750 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《考迪》是一部讲述战争如何留下伤痕的短篇故事，那些伤痕不仅刻在大地之上，也刻在人心之中。作为考迪对掸邦战争胜利的关键角色，巴伦踏上了归乡之路，心里充满愧疚、痛苦与怀疑；支撑他的友情支离破碎，对帝国的忠心摇摇欲坠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与形形色色的人物互动。人们以独特的视角诉说战争带来的毁灭，拼凑成一段有关沦亡、尊严与宽恕的故事……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏以独特的美术风格呈现，并将传统的像素艺术与3D建模及特效相融合</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/75e1ab71aec2e37440872cf0a3573852.avif?t=1762688249\" width=1466 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在内心世界中，你将探索巴伦内心最深处的思绪。可以独自思考，也可以与其他人物互动，倾听他们震撼人心的见证。完成人们委托的任务，揭示更多隐藏的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/21228959d9cc108f667c3ad9ee6bf4c6.poster.avif?t=1762688249\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/21228959d9cc108f667c3ad9ee6bf4c6.webm?t=1762688249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/21228959d9cc108f667c3ad9ee6bf4c6.mp4?t=1762688249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/82b6907f14679b6668d62dc43969558d.avif?t=1762688249\" width=1466 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使战争结束，巴伦仍不得不在某些区域进行战斗。活用移动与战斗技巧，击败敌人，跨越重重障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/7cf6663c733b26763e62059ff7ea06e0.poster.avif?t=1762688249\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/7cf6663c733b26763e62059ff7ea06e0.webm?t=1762688249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/7cf6663c733b26763e62059ff7ea06e0.mp4?t=1762688249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/19fc9575a03a4eae7e3b6c8cac8d9221.avif?t=1762688249\" width=750 height=122 /></span></p>",
